<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johannes Renker, Pfarrer von St. Lorenz zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt das unpriesterliche Verhalten des Ulrich Bürglein mit und bittet, sich wegen dessen Versetzung an Bischof Albrecht von Bamberg zu wenden.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="120v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_241_r1l12"><expan>Meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu ſand </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l13">lorencʒen ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_241_r1l14">Erſamer lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . als eẅch wol <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd ercʒelt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt vvıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l15">ſıch <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Bürgleıns . gar <expan>vnprıeſt<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> vnd <expan>vnördenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> bey vns heltt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l16">mıt <expan>meng<ex>er</ex>ley</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als das teglıch an vns kombt . Des wır niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l17"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſehen noch hören . Vnd auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> vnd ein gancʒ <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l18">ʒu eẅch <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ eẅch das auch laıd vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ſey . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l19">wır eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ Jr wellet daran gemant ſein . Ob Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l20">gen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> mıt fugen ſouıl gereden vnd getun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l21">möchtt Daʒ wır <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Bürglıns vnd ſeins <expan>vnördenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l22">lebens bey vns <expan>entlad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd quıtt <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſteen . Daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l23">tett Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rgot</expan> ein ere vnd <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>prıeſt<ex>er</ex>ſchaft</expan> bey vns wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l24">vnd vns <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> lıeb vnd <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> daʒ wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l25"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Martınj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="120v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu sand
                        Lorenczen zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer, lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ewch wol
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und erczelt
                                <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, wie sich
                            <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Bürgleins gar
                            <expan>unpriest<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> und
                            <expan>unördenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> bey uns heltt mit
                                <expan>meng<ex>er</ex>ley</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> als das teglich an uns kombt, des wir niht
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sehen noch hören und auch wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und ein gancz
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> zu ewch
                            <expan>habe<ex>n,</ex></expan> daz ewch das auch laid und
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> sey, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                        fleiss, ir wellet daran gemant sein, ob ir gen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> mit fugen
                        sovil gereden und getun möchtt, daz wir <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Bürglins und seins
                                <expan>unördenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lebens bey uns
                                <expan>entlad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> und quitt <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        steen. Daran tett ir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rgot</expan> ein ere und <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>priest<ex>er</ex>schaft</expan> bey uns wol und uns
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> lieb und
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Martini. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
